# G-INT-2 — LIVE STAGE-2 CAUSAL-ABLATION RECALL GATE (Phase B, Step 3)

Build: `_disp_build.bat` -> DISP_BUILD_DONE_0, clean compile (cargo, target-wirecuda, only pre-existing warnings).
Run: ONE daemon boot, gemma4-12b-b1.sp-model, SP_INT2=1 W=91 K=91 TAU=-8.0 M_target=42, registry=_needle_corpus_div (91 episodes: 90 div needles + ctrl_paris). temp=0, auto_recall=true, SP_B3_WC unset.
Default-off (SP_INT2 unset) = the prior path untouched = byte-identical null floor.

